reviewText: My grand daughter loves watching babies as she calls it lol . Love all the sons from Sunday school .

This Baby Praise (30 mins) is old rendition of Christian songs of the 90s. certainly not 2000s, BUT my babies like faces so I wanted to complete her collection of songs, praising our Father in Christ Jesus. it has more energetic and dancing songs than praise baby collection i own. i hold my baby upright and wiggle her as she laughs. I sing too like a prayer. my daughter goos and i thank God for her with a singing heart. note: im a stay-at-home mom so i review when my baby likes something. im typing while holding her.
